      "n": 1,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Kariza akunda kubaza\nAuthor - Jean de Dieu Bavugempore\nIllustrator - Rob Owen\nLanguage - Kinyarwanda\nLevel - Longer paragraphs\n© African Storybook Initiative, 2017\nCreative Commons: Attribution 4.0\nSource www.africanstorybook.org"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Kariza yakundaga kubaza. Uwo muco yawukomoye ku babyeyi be.\nBakundaga kumubwira bati: \"Nutabaza ukiri muto, uzasaza utamenye.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Umunsi umwe, Kariza yabajije mwarimu ati: \"Kubera iki buri gihe ababyeyi bacu badutegeka gukaraba intoki intoki mbere yo kurya, n'ubwo zaba zisa neza?\"\nBagenzi be bishimiye icyo kibazo. Na bo ntibakundaga kubwirizwa gukaraba."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Nuko Mwarimu aramusubiza ati: \"Ubajije ikibazo kiza Kari. Burya n'ubwo intoki zacu tuba tubona zisa neza, hari ubwo ziba ziriho udukoko tutagaragara.\"\nMwarimu akomeza gusobanura ati: \"Utwo dukoko dutera indwara kandi ntituboneshwa amaso yacu. Hari ibikoresho byabugenewe byifashishwa mu kutureba.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Mwarimu akura mikorosikopi mu kabati ati: \"Mikorosikopi ni igikoresho twifashisha tureba utuntu duto cyane tudashobora kuboneshwa amaso.\"\nMwarimu asharuza agati buhoro ku ntoki za Kariza hanyuma azirebera muri mikorosikopi."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Mwarimu yereka abanyeshuri ibyo mikorosikopi yerekana byavuye ku ntoki za Kariza.N'ubwo nta mwanda wagaragaraga ku ntoki, babonyeho udukoko twavuyeho."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Mwarimu akomeza abigisha ati: \"Mu bidukikije hose habamikorobe zitagaragara. Ibyo dukoraho mu ishuri, mu kibuga dukina, n'imuhara iwacu ziba ziriho, kandi izo mikorobe ni zo zidutera indwara.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Yungamo ati: \"Tugomba rero gukaraba intoki n'amazi meza n'isabuni, kugira ngo mikorobe ziriho zipfe. Ibyo tukabikora cyane cyane mbere yo kurya. No mu gihe turwaye tugomba kwibuka gukaraba kugira ngo tudakwirakwira izo mikorobe zitera indwara.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Kariza avuye ku ishuri yasanze se ari kubaka igikoresho giteye amatasiko. Aramubaza ati: \"Iki ni igiki uri gukora papa?\"\nSe aramubwira ati: \"Iki gikoresho kitwa Kandagirukarabe. Ni icyo tuzajya dukoresha dukaraba mu gihe tuvuye mu musarani, ndetse na mbere yo kurya.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Kariza abyumvise, aratangara ati: \"Yego koko! Uzi ko mwarimu wacu yayitubwiye! Ariko abenshi muri twe ntituzi uko ikoreshwa. Bayikoresha bate papa?\"\nSe araseka maze aramubwira ati: \"Igira hino mbikwereke mwana wa!\""
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Ati: \"Ngaho banza ukandagire kuri aka gati kari hasi.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Akomeza amubwira ati: \"Iyi jerekani irimo amazi irahita ihengama isuke amazi ku ntoki zawe maze ukarabe. Wibuke no gukoresha isabuni.\""
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Kariza biramushimisha cyane aravuga ati: \"Iyo ntaza kubaza ibi nari kubimenya nte? Burya koko kubaza bitera kumenya!\""
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Ibibazo\n1. Inkuru twasomye yitwa ngwiki?2. Ni akahe kamaro ko kubaza?3. Ni iyihe mpamvu dukaraba inoki mbere yo kurya?4. Ni iyihe mpamvu dukaraba inoki tuvuye ku musarani?\n5. Ni akahe kamaro ka Mikorosikopi?"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "img": null,
      "text": "Ibibazo\n6. Igihe tudakarabye inoki haba iki?7. Mikorobe ziva hehe?8. Kandagirukarabe ni iki?9. Ni ibihe bikoresho bikoreshwa mw’isuku?10. Ni bande bavuzwe mu nkuru?"
    },
